{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1775221522.263112", "card_id": "Q_2023391802560962717", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 167}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "贵州一县委书记闭幕致辞火了，全程 6 秒仅说两个字，这一极简致辞为何能火？折射出公众怎样的情绪？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "3 月 30 日傍晚，贵州黔东南州「州长杯」班超足球超级联赛榕江赛区闭幕式上，榕江县委书记徐勃走上球场，拿起话筒只说了「闭幕」二字，整个过程仅 6 秒，让现场的群众一愣，随后爆发出热烈掌声和笑声。 现场视频截图 4 月 3 日，极目新闻记者联系到视频中摆放话筒的组委会导演组的杨亚江，据他回忆，当时他话筒还没有完全摆好，县委书记徐勃就走过去说了「闭幕」两个字。下场后，徐勃与大家交流时表示，时间晚了，大家都累了，希望可以让大家早点回去休息，太晚路上不安全，他让大家赶快回家。 杨亚江还介绍，在 3 月 21 日的开幕式上，徐勃也只说了「开幕」两个字，原本预案是让他简单讲几句鼓励一下大家，再宣布开幕，但他只说了两个字，「没想到闭幕也这样，太简洁明了，出乎我们的预料，我肚子都笑疼了。」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-3d45b3b38285d1e9dd1116836ff32ff9_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "526 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2023391802560962717"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIkpT3/4P3nN5REAMaCTExOTAwODQ1NyDWoL3OBjAAONoCQAByEzIwMjMzOTE4MDI1NjA5NjI3MTd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1775221522.264573", "card_id": "Q_2022335697135179126", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 80}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "神似拉夫劳伦的品牌「保罗散步」常年打一折，单平台月销超两千万，「像素级复刻 + 极致低价」的模式能走多远？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "「保罗散步」正在迎来它的春天。该服装品牌原名 POLOWALK，从产品、 LOGO 到门店风格都幻视拉夫劳伦，但几乎只有后者十分之一的价格。 早年它的标志与一众山寨拉夫劳伦一起频繁出现在「如何辨认正品」的游戏中，玩笑间网友赐名「保罗散步」「保罗溜弯」。但慢慢地，人们的态度好像变了。 玩梗以外，更多的人穿上了保罗散步，还将它穿去了 CBD 和高端商场。他们说，「要拒绝保罗散步羞耻」。「保罗散步」迎来春天：「拉夫劳伦平替」常年打一折，单平台月销近 2500 万"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-6b2a08094d1ddda762a14970f94bb0d1_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "361 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2022335697135179126"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIkpT3/4P3nN5REAMaCTExODk3MDM4NCDD8a3OBjAAOIgCQAFyEzIwMjIzMzU2OTcxMzUxNzkxMjZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1775221522.265255", "card_id": "Q_2023407372723332647", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "苹果被曝高价扫荡全球手机内存，不惜牺牲利润锁死对手供应链，内存价格会再度暴涨吗？对安卓阵营冲击有多大？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "苹果公司被曝正在以极高价格收购市面上所有可用移动 DRAM 芯片 财联社 4 月 3 日消息，据韩国知情人士透露，苹果公司正在以极高的价格收购市面上所有可用的移动 DRAM 芯片，甚至不惜牺牲部分运营利润，这样可以阻止竞争对手获得足够的内存芯片。这一猜测与今年 1 月知名分析师郭明錤的想法几乎一致。当时，郭明錤就曾认为，内存涨价会影响苹果的毛利率，但吸收成本将有助于占领更大市场份额，且苹果可以通过服务来弥补损失。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-7c5e7d2cc22377fcd76c45fd93db5870_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "156 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2023407372723332647"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIkpT3/4P3nN5REAMaCTExOTAwOTE4NyDWvb3OBjAAOGxAAnITMjAyMzQwNzM3MjcyMzMzMjY0N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1775221522.265776", "card_id": "Q_2021907413951882731", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 48}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么国外的家都喜欢暖光，但国内却喜欢冷白光？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-b3e7b69b360216caa169ff3ff89576c7_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "133 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2021907413951882731"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIkpT3/4P3nN5REAMaCTExODk1MzU3OCDk06fOBjAAOIcBQANyEzIwMjE5MDc0MTM5NTE4ODI3MzF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1775221522.266086", "card_id": "Q_2023487705594565971", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 72}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "乒乓世界杯 1/8 决赛，王楚钦最终以 4 比 2 战胜小勒布伦，如何评价本场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f3120635c5e4ea0831f81d724edeefa6_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "104 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2023487705594565971"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIkpT3/4P3nN5REAMaCTExOTAxMjU2MCCn077OBjAAOE9ABHITMjAyMzQ4NzcwNTU5NDU2NTk3MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1775221522.266472", "card_id": "Q_2023397131986170111", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 103}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价伊朗再次声称又击落一架美军 F35 战斗机？这次 F35 战斗机可能是如何被击落的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "新华社德黑兰 4 月 3 日电 伊朗伊斯兰革命卫队公共关系部门 3 日发表声明说，防空系统在伊朗中部领空击落一架美国 F－35 战斗机。 声明说，该战斗机已被「完全摧毁并坠落」，战机已解体，飞行员下落不明。声明还说，这是伊斯兰革命卫队防空系统过去 12 小时内击落的第二架美国战机。 「这是我们对美国总统特朗普胡言乱语的首次回应。」声明写道。 伊朗媒体公布了战机解体碎片的照片，并表示飞行员生还几率很低。 伊朗伊斯兰革命卫队公共关系部门 2 日说，一架「先进的敌方战机」在霍尔木兹海峡附近的格什姆岛南部被伊方防空系统击中，该战机随后坠入波斯湾水域。美军中央司令部随后予以否认，称所有美军战斗机均处于「可查状态」。伊朗说击落又一架美军战机 - 新华网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d447839b7e4213576053abc2a6eb0ba7_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "98 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2023397131986170111"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIkpT3/4P3nN5REAMaCTExOTAwODYzNyDNqr3OBjAAOP8BQAVyEzIwMjMzOTcxMzE5ODYxNzAxMTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1775221522.267388", "card_id": "Q_2000359413463159387", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待菲尔兹得主带头，千余数学家抵制在美举办国际数学家大会？对 2026 年国际数学家大会产生什么影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "法国数学会的官方通知:Title: La SMF n『ira pas à l』ICM de Philadelphie La SMF ne tiendra pas de stand à l『ICM de Philadelphie. En effet ni la délivrance de visas par le pays hôte, ni sa sécurité intérieure alors qu』y EST régulièrement évoquée la loi martiale, ne semblent garanties. Par ailleurs la SMF reste fondamentalement attachée à l『héritage de Benjamin Franklin, inséparable de la pensée rationnelle, et condamne la défiance envers la science et toute atteinte aux libertés académiques. (Motion du Conseil d』administration du 16 janvier 2026)"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-4442fc10cab0a26c05cae19fc29f83d4_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "93 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2000359413463159387"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIkpT3/4P3nN5REAMaCTExODI1OTA5OCDBi+7LBjAAOOgBQAZyEzIwMDAzNTk0MTM0NjMxNTkzODd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1775221522.268539", "card_id": "Q_2022969399204751300", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 138}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么游戏里魔法师永远是体弱、脆皮、拄拐杖的刻板印象？有没有肌肉、近战、狂战士型的反套路魔法师？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7ef2dd20c318d3993ff0c38863726ebc_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "88 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2022969399204751300"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIkpT3/4P3nN5REAMaCTExODk5MDkxMSD